project_descr: Capacity Development for National SDGs Adaptation. The Goal of the Project is to support the Government to enhance national capacities and raise awareness on SDG-based issues.

outputs.output_descr: Capacity Development for National Sustainable Development Goals Adaptation. The Government has demonstrated full commitment to the implementation of SDGs and clearly benefited from UN support to integrate the SDGs into upcoming strategic development cycle.
